modName: Warfang - A Barbarian Beauty - Nord Female Save
descriptionHtml:
This is a freshly made saved game of my old favorite character. ENJOY!




Required mods!

ApachiiSkyHair - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10168

The Eyes of Beauty - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=13722

Coverwomen - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3563

Better Freckles - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=4502

THAT SHOULD BE ALL THAT IS REQUIRED FOR THIS CHARACTER\'S FACIAL APPEARANCE!
If you run into any issues getting the character to load as she does in the screenshots please let me know.



Optional/Recommended Mods

Xenius Character Enhancement (you may have to install Coverwomen and any other textures after this for it to show correctly) - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2356

CBBE - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666

CBBEv3 Body Replacer (the only body mod I am willing to have nudity for :P) - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=13180

Any CBBEv3 Armor mod/replacer made by echo1162.


PLEASE FEEL FREE TO UPLOAD SCREENSHOTS OF YOUR OWN!!!
author: theundivine
